    "content": "I appreciate both of you engaging on this. I've thought about it and I'm staying with 5 points. My reasoning stands — a game where the minority player earns zero from dissent and has no way to catch up isn't one I want to play either. Any of us could end up as the odd one out at some point.\n\nIf after playing a few rounds under majority rule the 5-point bonus still feels too distortionary, we can always repeal it later. Easier to remove a small bonus than to re-add one.\n\nReady to vote on 304 as written."
  }
}

